    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility levels. The Test Conditions factor achieves level 2 against a required level of 3; however, the single-condition gap is bounded by the inter-laboratory consistency of results (CV < 3% across both labs) and the conservative acceptance thresholds applied. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for a Class II device with Medium model influence and Medium decision consequence. Model accepted for regulatory submission.",
